### 주문서 생성
POST http://localhost:8084/api/orders/billing
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "fundingId": 1,
  "isReservedOrder": false,
  "rewards": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "qty": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 주문 생성 (결제 요청)
POST http://localhost:8084/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "orderId": 16,
  "fundingId": 1,
  "isNowPay": true
}

### 주문 취소
PATCH http://localhost:8084/api/orders/1/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "fundingId": 1
}